Sisca "Chika" Jessica (amụrụ n'Eprel 25, nà afọ 1988) bụ onye Indonesia na-eme ihe nkiri nke a maara nke ọma maka ọrụ ya dị ka onye na-akwado ihe ngosi Hitam Putih Talk nke Deddy Corbuzier kwadoro. Ọ malitere ọrụ ya site na ọrụ na ihe nkiri soap opera. N'afọ 2009, ọ pụtara na ihe nkiri Merantau ya na Iko Uwais na Christine Hakim
